com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium

Enum EditorCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EditorCommand>
      • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.EditorCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable< EditorCommand> 

    public enum EditorCommand
extends java.lang.Enum<EditorCommand>
    The list of commands for text manipulation when editing in a text field, text area or WYSIWYG editor. Also contains more common commands like Cut, Copy, Paste, SelectAll, Undo, Redo, which can be executed for the frame in the loaded web page.
    在文本字段，文本区域或WYSIWYG编辑器中进行编辑时，用于文本操作的命令列表。还包含更常见的命令，例如剪切，复制，粘贴，SelectAll，撤消，重做，可以对已加载的网页中的框架执行这些命令。

      • FIND_STRING

        public static final EditorCommand FIND_STRING
        Searches for the next string occurrence from the current caret position in the loaded web page. If match found, this command will select it and scroll down to make it visible, if needed.
        从加载的网页中的当前插入符号位置搜索下一个出现的字符串。如果找到匹配项，则此命令将选择它并向下滚动以使其可见（如果需要）。
